    {"Equipment": "Bench Press", "Muscle": "Triceps", "Exercise": "Close-grip Bench Press", "Instructions": "Grip the barbell with your hands positioned close together, lower it to your chest, and press it back up. This targets the triceps, while also engaging the chest."},
    {"Equipment": "Bench Press", "Muscle": "Triceps", "Exercise": "Tricep Extension", "Instructions": "Lie on a flat bench and hold the barbell with your arms extended overhead. Lower the bar behind your head by bending your elbows, then press it back overhead to the starting position. This exercise isolates the triceps."},
    {"Equipment": "Bench Press", "Muscle": "Triceps", "Exercise": "Skull Crusher", "Instructions": "Lie on a bench and hold the barbell with your arms extended overhead. Lower the barbell towards your forehead by bending your elbows. Press the barbell back to the starting position. This exercise isolates the triceps."},
