    {"Equipment": "Dumbbell", "Muscle": "Full Body", "Exercise": "Dumbbell Clean and Press", "Instructions": "Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and a dumbbell in each hand. Lower into a squat and explosively stand up, bringing the dumbbells to shoulder height. Press the dumbbells overhead. Lower the weights back down to your sides. This full-body exercise targets the shoulders, legs, and core."},
    {"Equipment": "Dumbbell", "Muscle": "Full Body", "Exercise": "Renegade Row", "Instructions": "Start in a plank position, with a dumbbell in each hand. Row one dumbbell towards your torso while stabilizing with the other arm. Lower the dumbbell back to the floor, and repeat on the other side. This exercise works the upper back, arms, and core."},
    {"Equipment": "Dumbbell", "Muscle": "Legs", "Exercise": "Goblet Squat", "Instructions": "Hold a dumbbell with both hands close to your chest, keeping your elbows pointed down. Lower into a squat by bending your knees and hips, keeping your chest up and back straight. Press through your heels to stand back up. This exercise targets the quads, glutes, and core."},
