    {"Equipment": "Pull-up Bar", "Muscle": "Back", "Exercise": "Chin-up", "Instructions": "Grip the pull-up bar with your palms facing toward you. Hang with your arms fully extended, then pull your chin over the bar. Lower your body back down with control. This exercise targets the biceps, lats, and upper back."},
